Welcome to BlogEngine2 0.9.8!

BlogEngine2 is a lightweight microblogging toolkit for Django.

A live demo is here: https://www.isotopesoftware.ca/blog/

Features:
 * Messages, Comments
 * RSS support 
 * Durus backward compatibility
 * ZODB (ClientStorage) support through Schevo API (requires libschevo 4.1)
 * OAuth 2.0 support
 * Libauthkit support
